{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Space Bross</strong></i> is a thrilling blend of action <strong><i>2.5D roguelite,</i></strong><i>\u00a0and\u00a0</i><strong><i>Tower Defense</i></strong><i>\u00a0</i>genres. Step into the boots of a retired astronaut whose mission has turned personal, your beloved chicken has been abducted by aliens. Now, driven by vengeance and the hope of reunion, you must traverse strange and hostile planets, survive relentless waves of enemies, and uncover clues in the vast, unforgiving expanse of space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962280/extras/Strategize.png?t=1735548448\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962280/extras/Turret.gif?t=1735548448\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare for battle by strategically placing turrets and building a strong base. Plan ahead, use your resources wisely, and fortify your defenses as you gear up to face incoming enemies. The success of your strategy will determine whether you can hold the line or fall to the horde.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962280/extras/Fight.png?t=1735548448\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962280/extras/Fight_Scene.gif?t=1735548448\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Arm yourself and dive into combat as waves of enemies come crashing down. Use your firepower to defeat them and collect loot from each victory. Use these rewards to enhance your character, improve your weapons, and upgrade your turrets, making you even stronger for the battles to come.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962280/extras/Evolve.png?t=1735548448\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962280/extras/Base.gif?t=1735548448\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Invest your hard-earned resources in the tech tree to unlock powerful upgrades. Evolve your equipment, weapons, and base to increase your chances of survival. As you progress, your gear will become more advanced, giving you the edge you need to conquer tougher enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962280/extras/Character_Evolve.gif?t=1735548448\" />\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962280/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735548448","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962280/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735548448","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962280/4a4248c91896046ade061768c6684676df4809ad/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735548448","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962280/4a4248c91896046ade061768c6684676df4809ad/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735548448","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Space Bross</strong></i> is a thrilling blend of action <strong><i>2.5D roguelite,</i></strong><i>\u00a0and\u00a0</i><strong><i>Tower Defense</i></st